text: Rubio's Coastal Grill is an American fast casual restaurant chain. It specializes in Mexican food, with an emphasis on fish tacos. It has more than 200 restaurants in Arizona, California, Florida, Colorado, Nevada, and Utah. It is headquartered in Carlsbad, California. It was founded in 1983.
